We’ve tuned our PID for PathPlanner, and initially, it produces clean runs. However, randomly, the XY error begins to spike and oscillate, even though no changes have been made. This issue occurs both in simulation and on our actual robot.
I have attached a photo below. You can see the different between the first and second runs.

Screenshot 2025-02-08 1652121915×1136 152 KB

Sometimes, there will also be a huge spike in front. Which I cannot attach right now.
